snippet.title: Slender Man: Rise Again Android HD GamePlay Trailer
snippet.description:
FOR MORE TOP & BEST ANDROID GAMES GO: http://goo.gl/SIElqH
FOLLOW ME ON TWITTER: https://goo.gl/KBhH7G


This is Slender Man: Rise Again! (Free version with ads)
There is an ads-free version to buy, if you want.
This is a brand new Slender Man game that will scare all the fans out there.
It almost feels as if you really walking in the fog and being hunted by Slender.
The atmosphere is scary.
In this free version there are two playable levels: "Field" and "Village"
If you like this game, give it a high rating, thanks!
Thank you all for your high ratings and nice reviews!
Enjoy!


Download link:  https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dvloper.slendermanriseagainfree
